Immerse yourself in a world of seamless connectivity with an advanced home network infrastructure, courtesy of ATT, ensuring your digital life runs effortlessly. Plus, the home is Alexa-wired. Every electrical enhancement in this home exceeds national safety standards. The upgraded A/C unit boasts a UV standard Green UV feature, ensuring not only comfort but also a healthy indoor environment. The Ring camera systems come with the property, a comprehensive spec sheet for the home, complete with receipts, details of upgrades, and even paint colors, is readily available. This level of transparency ensures you're fully informed about the value. Welcome to the epitome of modern living in this exceptional two-story townhouse, originally constructed in 2017 but now fully reimagined and upgraded to meet the demands of today's discerning homeowner.
Immerse yourself in a world of seamless connectivity with an advanced home network infrastructure, courtesy of ATT, ensuring your digital life runs effortlessly. Plus, the home is Alexa-wired. With ATT's fiberoptic ready connection, you'll experience fast internet speeds for all your streaming and smart home needs.
As you step inside, be greeted by an abundance of light in the living room, thanks to the newly installed lights complete with dimmers, setting the perfect ambiance for any occasion. Every electrical enhancement in this home exceeds national safety standards.
The upgraded A/C unit boasts a UV standard Green UV feature, ensuring not only comfort but also a healthy indoor environment.
The garage features an epoxy finish and including practical additions such as red storage bins, hurricane panels, and a stowaway workbench, all included in the sale. You'll also appreciate the fully insulated "MyQ" integrated garage door, which not only adds to your convenience but also reduces heat transfer from the outside.
For enhanced security and peace of mind, the Ring camera systems come with the property, providing you with a watchful eye over your home.
To make your life even easier, a comprehensive spec sheet for the home, complete with receipts, details of upgrades, and even paint colors, is readily available. This level of transparency ensures you're fully informed about the value and care that's gone into this home.
Don't miss this opportunity to own a townhouse that effortlessly combines form and function, making it a truly exceptional place to call home.
